name: title
Gatto 5mm beam PCCD3 9wks: Kinematic of 9-week-old PCCD3 mice walking on a 5 mm wide beam

name: description
Gatto 5mm beam PCCD3 9wks: Original SIMI videos, DeepLabCut-tracked videos and csv files of body kinematics of 9-week-old ChAT-Dre;Pitx2-Cre;R26-LSL-RSR-hM3D::zsGreen mice walking on a wide 5 mm beam. Control Group. Individual trials for each mouse are recorded from 8 cameras and metadata for synchronization is stored as *.smp files.
